name: Senior #5 - Timo
description:
Timo is a 73-year-old former soccer referee who enjoys Chinese food, running and hair styling. He is warm-hearted and handsome, but can also be very dramatic and a bit dumb.

He is currently single. His most recent romance was with a cleaner called Edna, who was 18 years older than him. They broke up because Edna wanted somebody more intellectual.
